        "text": "MiroShark gained its 32nd catalogued surface — GET /api/status.json. A dedicated health endpoint for external status monitors (Upptime, BetterUptime, Statuspage.io) and ecosystem integrators to pre-flight check the deployment. Returns a live envelope: ok flag, queue depth, 24h completions, lifetime sim total, surface count. No in-process cache (30s HTTP cache only). Empty deployments return the all-zero envelope, never 404.",
        "variant": "body"
      }
